<div class="desc-container">
  <div class="desc-card">
    <span class="desc-icon">🎮</span>
    <span class="desc-text">御三家全制霸·次元壁穿梭者</span>
  </div>
  <div class="desc-card">
    <span class="desc-icon">🏍️</span>
    <span class="desc-text">跨上铁骑追逐地平线的冒险家</span>
  </div>
  <div class="desc-card">
    <span class="desc-icon">💻</span>
    <span class="desc-text">用键盘编织代码的二进制诗人</span>
  </div>
  <div class="desc-card">
    <span class="desc-icon">⚽️</span>
    <span class="desc-text">二十年美凌格·银河战舰永不沉没</span>
  </div>
  <div class="desc-card">
    <span class="desc-icon">✒️</span>
    <span class="desc-text">执钢笔写春秋的器物美学家</span>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .desc-container {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 0.8s ease-out 0.4s forwards;
  }
  .desc-card {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    padding: 0.6rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 12px;
    background: rgb(var(--color-bg-body));
    border: 1px solid rgb(var(--color-text-muted) / 0.08);
    transition: all 0.25s ease;
    max-width: 28rem;
    width: 100%;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  .desc-card:hover {
    border-color: rgb(var(--color-primary-blue) / 0.3);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgb(var(--color-primary-blue) / 0.08);
  }
  .desc-icon {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .desc-text {
    color: rgb(var(--color-text-body));
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  @keyframes fadeUp {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(12px); }
    to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }
</style>
